            "value" : "屏幕录制"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Screen Recording is only needed for menu bar item previews in Layout. Folding still works without it." : {
      "comment" : "Explanation shown in Settings > Permissions for the optional Screen Recording permission.",
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "画面収録は、レイアウトでメニューバー項目のプレビューを表示する場合にのみ必要です。折りたたみ機能はこの権限がなくても動作します。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "屏幕录制仅用于在布局中预览菜单栏项目。没有此权限时，折叠功能仍可工作。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Screen recording permissions are required to display tooltips." : {
      "comment" : "A message displayed in the \"Permissions\" section of the advanced settings pane, explaining that screen recording permissions are needed to show tooltips.",
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ツールチップを表示するには、画面収録の権限が必要です。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
