        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "按住 Option 键点按以打开永久隐藏区域"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use the faster LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) algorithm for profile sorting on notched displays instead of the full sort. LCS minimises the number of moves but may be less reliable on notched displays with smaller resolutions." : {
      "comment" : "A tooltip that explains the purpose of a setting.",
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ノッチ付きディスプレイでのプロファイル並び替えにおいて、完全ソートの代わりに高速な LCS（最長共通部分列）アルゴリズムを使用します。LCS は移動回数を最小限に抑えますが、解像度の低いノッチ付きディスプレイでは精度が低下する場合があります。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在带刘海的显示器上，对配置排序时使用更快的 LCS（最长公共子序列）算法，而不是完整排序。LCS 可减少项目移动次数，但在分辨率较低的带刘海显示器上可能稳定性较差。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Version %@ (%@)" : {
      "comment" : "A label displaying the current version and build number of the app. The first argument is the version string. The second argument is the build string.",
